	('Ellen, you, you, oh','Ellen, là chị, là chị, ôi','00:12:18.000','00:12:21.400','english-fairy-tales-2'),
	('Are you alright?','Em có sao không?','00:12:22.000','00:12:23.800','english-fairy-tales-2'),
