	('Where is the gold?','Vàng đâu rồi?','00:10:55.790','00:10:57.110','english-fairy-tales-11'),
	('How could you?','Sao các cậu lại làm thế?','00:10:57.250','00:10:58.290','english-fairy-tales-11'),
