	('Hmm','Ừm','00:11:11.130','00:11:12.110','english-fairy-tales-62'),
	('How long has it been?','Đã bao lâu rồi?','00:11:16.260','00:11:18.560','english-fairy-tales-62'),
	('Madam, the jeweler is here','Thưa bà, thợ kim hoàn đã đến','00:11:20.980','00:11:24.260','english-fairy-tales-62'),
	('Hmm?','Ừm?','00:11:24.800','00:11:25.220','english-fairy-tales-62'),
	('Oh, how wonderful','Ồ, thật tuyệt vời','00:11:25.800','00:11:27.740','english-fairy-tales-62'),
	('Bring him in','Đưa ông ấy vào','00:11:28.500','00:11:29.360','english-fairy-tales-62'),
	('Hello, mother, father','Xin chào mẹ, cha','00:11:30.760','00:11:33.240','english-fairy-tales-62'),
	('Hiroshi','Hiroshi','00:11:35.340','00:11:36.400','english-fairy-tales-62'),
	('Oh, Hiroshi','Ôi, Hiroshi','00:11:36.840','00:11:38.380','english-fairy-tales-62'),
	('Hiroshi','Hiroshi','00:11:38.380','00:11:38.580','english-fairy-tales-62'),
	('Hiroshi hugged his mother tightly, and although his father was silent, Hiroshi knew he cared','Hiroshi ôm mẹ thật chặt, và mặc dù cha cậu im lặng, Hiroshi biết ông vẫn quan tâm','00:11:38.760','00:11:44.320','english-fairy-tales-62'),
